    RETRIEVE_BTC_PROCESS_IDS,
    \* Same as for retrieve_btc, just for the resubmit_retrieve_btc minter method.
    \* @type: Set(PID);
    RESUBMIT_RETRIEVE_BTC_PROCESS_IDS,
    \**********************************************************************************************
    \* Other constants
